
"Can we eat him too?" The third wondered.
Gandalf split the huge boulder. Sunlight hit the trolls and turned them into stone. I used one of my throwing knives to cut the sack. I helped free the others. Haley and Blake appeared from behind Gandalf. I hugged them both. Gandalf and Thorin talked some. Thorin found a cave. I staid outside with Fili and Kili.
Thorin came out with the Orcist in his hand. He handed it to me. "You need it more then me." Thorin smiled. I kissed his cheek. I whispered my thanks in his ear.
"Someone is coming." Blake said.
